name: LUCKY BASTARD
description: The motorcycle is the Harley-Davidson Sportster 883 that Carmichael Lynch owned when I worked on the Harley-Davidson account around about the time of the Dark Custom launch (2009?) It was beaten and shitty and nobody wanted to ride it so I asked if I could chop it, repaint it and make it rock. They let me. It kicked ass. It was so fucking loud and cool looking when I was done with it that everyone wanted to ride it. We called it "Lucky Bastard."
